Join Operations
Data Prep supports these join operations.
Lookup: returns all rows from the left data stream and only matching rows from the right data stream.
Left Join: includes all rows from the left and only matching rows from the right.
Right Join: includes all rows from the right and only matching rows from the left.
Inner Join: includes only matching rows from the left and right.
Full Outer Join: includes all rows from the left and right, regardless of whether they have matches.
Cross Join: combines unrelated records and includes all rows from the left and the right.

Considerations When Using Joins
In CRM Analytics, unlike a lookup, a join creates a separate record for each match in the target dataset when multiple rows match.
